sentence.text: To gain an insight into the likely molecular basis of their observed cytotoxic effects, Autodock Vina binding free energies of each of the isolated compounds with seven molecular targets implicated in cancer development (MAPK8, protein phosphorylation, MAP3K12, MAPK3, protein phosphorylation, MAPK7 and negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II), were calculated.

entity.text: negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II
